	"Analog Modulation:PM:PM Enabled [PM]"
	bool readwrite local 001312EF
"Specifies whether the signal generator applies phase modulation to the RF output signal (TRUE) or not (FALSE).
VI_TRUE 1
True

VI_FALSE 0
False"
attribute: "PM Source [PM]"
	"Analog Modulation:PM:PM Source [PM]"
	string readwrite local 001312F0
"Specifies the source of the signal that is used as the modulating signal. If more than one source is specified, the voltages of all sources (internal and external) are summed.  Multiple source names are separated by commas."
attribute: "PM External Coupling [PM]"
	"Analog Modulation:PM:PM External Coupling [PM]"
	iL enum { IVIRFSIGGEN_VAL_PM_EXTERNAL_COUPLING_AC=1, IVIRFSIGGEN_VAL_PM_EXTERNAL_COUPLING_DC=2} readwrite local 001312F1
"Specifies the coupling of the external source of the modulating signal.
IVIRFSIGGEN_VAL_PM_EXTERNAL_COUPLING_AC 1
